Final Reflection

You will choose your top three projects to reflect on here. Please answer the following questions for each project:

  1. How did your knowledge of Social Studies grow by doing this project?

  2. What important lessons about time management did you learn from doing this project and any other skills that you needed to develop along the way to complete it successfully?

  3. What challenges did you face and how did you overcome them?

  4. What did you enjoy most about creating this project?
